menuconfig BR2_PACKAGE_ABDUCO
	bool "abduco"
	help
		abduco provides session management i.e. it allows programs to be run independently from their 
		controlling terminal. That is programs can be detached - run in the background - and then later 
		reattached. Together with dvtm it provides a simpler and cleaner alternative to tmux or screen.

		https://www.brain-dump.org/projects/abduco
